      "date": "2015-01-14 18:11:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThe move of the check to the beginning of the test is incorrect - the test on the local node's /proc should always work, so it should always be run. The test should only be skipped for remote servers that have old versions of Lustre.",
