      "date": "2015-01-14 21:14:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nIt is probably reasonable then to split test_133g to 2 different tests: 1) \"local\"; 2) \"remote\"  to skip a full test instead of part of the test to provide the tests integrity. The current test version if run on interop setup with old server is always marked as \"skipped\" and results.yml file contains the confusing \"status: SKIP\".\nAndreas, if you agree with my thoughts -- I will file LU ticket for this 133g test modification.\nThanks.",
